---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PostCard from "@components/PostCard.astro";
import { getFeaturedPosts, getPublishedPosts } from "@lib/posts";

const featuredPosts = await getFeaturedPosts();
const posts = await getPublishedPosts();
const heroPost = featuredPosts[0] ?? posts[0];
const latestPosts = posts.filter((post) => post.id !== heroPost?.id).slice(0, 4);
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main>
    <section class="hero-wrap">
      <div class="site-shell hero">
        <div>
          <div class="category-tabs" aria-label="Categories">
            <a class="category-tab active" href="/posts/">Engineering</a>
            <a class="category-tab" href="/resume/">Resume</a>
            <a class="category-tab" href="/about/">About</a>
          </div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Backend Engineering Notes</p>
          <h1>운영에서 흔들리지 않는 백엔드 설계를 기록합니다.</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            이벤트 검수, 정산 비용확정, 송금 안정성, 인프라와 관측성을 중심으로
            도메인 상태와 운영 리스크를 함께 다룬 경험을 씁니다.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button primary" href="/posts/">아티클 읽기</a>
            <a class="button quiet" href="/resume/">이력 요약</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="profile-panel" aria-label="Profile summary">
          <img src="https://github.com/wonchangPark.png" alt="박원창 GitHub profile" />
          <div>
            <p class="profile-role">Backend Engineer</p>
            <h2>박원창</h2>
            <p>Java, Spring Boot, 정산, approval workflow, reliability, cloud infra.</p>
          </div>
          <dl class="metric-list">
            <div>
              <dt>PRs</dt>
              <dd>293+</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>Posts</dt>
              <dd>5</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>Focus</dt>
              <dd>Ops</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    {heroPost && (
      <section class="site-shell feature-section">
        <a class="featured-story article-link" href={`/posts/${heroPost.id}/`}>
          <div>
            <p class="article-meta">
              Featured · {heroPost.data.category} · {heroPost.data.author}
            </p>
            <h2>{heroPost.data.title}</h2>
            <p>
              {heroPost.data.description}
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-side">
            <span>{heroPost.data.pubDate.toLocaleDateString("ko-KR", {
              year: "numeric",
              month: "long",
              day: "numeric"
            })}</span>
            <strong>Read article</strong>
          </div>
        </a>
      </section>
    )}

    <section class="site-shell section article-section">
      <div class="section-header compact">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Latest</p>
          <h2>전체 아티클</h2>
        </div>
        <a class="text-link" href="/posts/">모두 보기</a>
      </div>
      <div class="post-list subtle-list">
        {latestPosts.map((post) => <PostCard post={post} />)}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="site-shell section">
      <div class="principles editorial-principles">
        <section class="principle">
          <span>01</span>
          <h3>상태 전이를 먼저 본다</h3>
          <p>데이터가 언제 바뀌고, 언제 더 이상 바뀌면 안 되는지를 기준으로 API와 테이블을 설계합니다.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="principle">
          <span>02</span>
          <h3>실패 경로를 데이터로 남긴다</h3>
          <p>외부 API와 비동기 작업은 실패를 전제로 두고 멱등성, outbox, retry 경로를 둡니다.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="principle">
          <span>03</span>
          <h3>운영자가 설명할 수 있게 만든다</h3>
          <p>승인, 송금, 비용확정처럼 민감한 작업은 이력과 산출 근거를 남겨 추적 가능하게 합니다.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
